WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.030
Alright truckers, listen up!

00:00:05.030 --> 00:00:07.400
The event you've been waiting for all year long

00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:09.340
is right around the corner.

00:00:09.340 --> 00:00:12.870
It's the 2012 Shell Rotella SuperRigs Event

00:00:12.870 --> 00:00:14.580
rolling into Joplin, Missouri

00:00:14.580 --> 00:00:17.810
May 17th to the 19th next to the Joplin Speedco.

00:00:17.810 --> 00:00:20.320
This year is really something special.

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:22.220
Not only is it the 30th Anniversary

00:00:22.220 --> 00:00:24.620
of the premiere truck beauty contest,

00:00:24.620 --> 00:00:26.920
but Shell Rotella SuperRigs and Speedco

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:28.920
are joining forces to support the

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:31.160
All Roads Lead to Joplin rebuilding project.

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:33.670
Truckers from all over the US and Canada

00:00:33.670 --> 00:00:36.000
arrive at this three day event for food,

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:37.930
games, entertainment and the chance

00:00:37.930 --> 00:00:41.150
to win over $25,000 dollars in cash and prizes,

00:00:41.150 --> 00:00:44.470
not to mention some serious bragging rights.

00:00:44.470 --> 00:00:46.910
Many will come, but only a few will be deemed

00:00:46.910 --> 00:00:49.110
super enough to be a Super Rig.

00:00:49.110 --> 00:00:51.850
Competition includes Best of Show, Tractor,

00:00:51.850 --> 00:00:54.880
Tractor Trailer and Classic Division categories.

00:00:54.880 --> 00:00:57.820
There are also awards for best theme, interior,

00:00:57.820 --> 00:01:00.820
chrome, lights, engine and the people's choice.

00:01:00.820 --> 00:01:04.900
Plus, 12 lucky contestants will be selected, photographed

00:01:04.900 --> 00:01:09.160
and featured in the 2013 Shell Rotella SuperRigs calendar.

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:13.280
More than national recognition, that's pin-up immortality.

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:16.000
And new this year, you can enter your truck online

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.270
in our Virtual Shell Rotella SuperRigs

00:01:18.270 --> 00:01:19.540
People's Choice contest.

00:01:19.540 --> 00:01:21.720
Just upload a pic of your prized rig

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:23.610
and let the voting begin.

00:01:23.610 --> 00:01:27.050
You just might win up to $500 in cash and prizes.

00:01:27.050 --> 00:01:29.620
Details at VirtualSuperRigs.com.

00:01:29.620 --> 00:01:34.020
Upload your rig at www.VirtualSuperRigs.com

00:01:34.020 --> 00:01:36.590
So mark your calendars, the Shell Rotella

00:01:36.590 --> 00:01:39.420
SuperRigs event is May 17th to the 19th

00:01:39.420 --> 00:01:41.230
and free to all participants.

00:01:41.230 --> 00:01:43.630
Pre-register for the event at Rotella.com

00:01:43.630 --> 00:01:46.370
by May 1st and you'll receive a VIP parking

00:01:46.370 --> 00:01:48.770
spot and premier contestant package.

00:01:48.770 --> 00:01:52.340
But, before you enter you have to ask yourself one thing.

00:01:52.340 --> 00:01:54.680
Is your truck worthy for SuperRigs?

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:59.210
However tough, Shell Rotella protects.

